#

Pumpkin Seed Stuffed Peppers

45 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyHealthyComfort Food

Description

Colorful bell peppers filled with a savory mix of pumpkin seeds, quinoa, and spices, baked to perfection!

Ingredients

  • bell peppers: 4
  • quinoa: 1 cup
  • pumpkin seeds: 1/2 cup
  • black beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • corn: 1 cup
  • onion: 1 small, diced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • chili powder: 1 tsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
